<body>
  <h1>Chocolate Cake Recipe</h1>

  <p>
    This delicious chocolate cake is easy to make and perfect for any occasion.
  </p>

  <img
    src="https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/labs/recipe.jpg"
    alt="A chocolate cake on a plate"
  >

  <h2>Ingredients</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>2 cups flour</li>
    <li>1 cup sugar</li>
    <li>3 eggs</li>
    <li>1 cup milk</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Instructions</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>Preheat the oven to 180°C.</li>
    <li>Mix all the ingredients in a bowl.</li>
    <li>Pour the mixture into a baking pan.</li>
    <li>Bake for 35 minutes.</li>
  </ol>
